alert.note: Alert for San Luis Obispo County Mountains; Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains; Santa Lucia Mountains (California) Issued by the National Weather Service

info.headline: High Wind Watch issued January 03 at 2:25PM PST until January 05 at 4:00AM PST by NWS Oxnard
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WATCH REMAINS IN EFFECT FROM WEDNESDAY MORNING THROUGH LATE WEDNESDAY NIGHT... * WHAT...South winds 35 to 50 mph with gusts up to 70 mph possible. * WHERE...Santa Lucia Mountains, San Luis Obispo County Mountains and Santa Barbara County Interior Mountains. * WHEN...From Wednesday morning through late Wednesday night. * IMPACTS...Damaging winds could blow down large objects such as trees and power lines. Power outages are possible. Travel could be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
info.instruction: Monitor the latest forecasts and warnings for updates on this situation. Fasten loose objects or shelter objects in a safe location prior to the onset of winds.
